The updated quote is a translation of what Croatian historian Rudolf Horvat wrote 23 years after the event.  This version is also most often presented in Croatian history books and media.  This quote more accurately and precisely represents the mood of the event.  The Croats did not protest against generic "militarism"  but against "Serbian militarism!" which was oppressing the Croats.
